{"tid":925672,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中俄比長短 雙方官媒互嗆戰機「垃圾」、「山寨機」","createTime":"2018-12-03T02:15:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-03T08:53:37.000Z","uid":28765,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"0cafe3461fe87ddf1c637fd9289633a9544299af","tid":925672,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T02:15:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php59rDtc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_php59rDtc.jpg&h=eef6a18d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國官媒嗆蘇-57戰機（左）垃圾；俄媒體批殲-20（右）山寨機。（美聯社，本報合成）<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國與俄羅斯雙方官媒近期內為了國產戰機吵得不可開交，互相指責對方的短處，同時誇耀自己的長處，中國媒體嗆俄方蘇-57戰機是垃圾，俄方媒體則批評中國的殲-20為山寨機。<br />\n<br />\n根據《自由亞洲電台》報導，中國11月在珠海舉辦航空展，同時讓全新的殲-20戰機亮相飛行，俄國各媒體後來提到與戰機出售相關事件時，均會提到俄國試飛員評價中國殲-20戰機是山寨機，使用大量俄國、美國戰機技術，不如俄羅斯國產的第5代戰機蘇-57。<br />\n<br />\n中國官媒對此不甘示弱，《新浪軍事》發布名為「俄新雷達研發10年測距160公里比中國低端貨少10公里」的報導，與俄方媒體互別苗頭，當中提到大酸俄國雷達技術長時間不如歐美地區國家，「電子工業太爛」，導致米格-35、蘇-57戰機隱身功能不甚理想。<br />\n<br />\n即使中國已經讓殲-20服役，仍然讓俄國方面嗤之以鼻，原因在於蘇-57戰機已在敘利亞戰場有所表現，但殲-20到目前為止缺乏實戰數據，且俄方專家尤里．古希科夫表示，俄羅斯目前已有嶄新雷達技術，能在戰機機身上布滿雷達，進行全方位探測，防衛功能大步提升。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2630861\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2630861&d=j2VufJ7sHyWA%2BEuaD8bPOU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=b6a995ca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2630861&h=acb45ca0\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2630861</a>"},{"pid":"6904cf7ba116fb547c5010aa449e6f64be691c01","tid":925672,"uid":29080,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T02:30:33.000Z","msg":"打過，睇下邊個勁啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aebe88d18fe572545d3dce87fd34f0761642920","tid":925672,"uid":75326,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T02:57:27.000Z","msg":"仲入緊S400<br />\n中國官媒死剩把口"},{"pid":"317d8421f0debc0fcb5a68e15e631e4566c16a32","tid":925672,"uid":88737,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T02:58:51.000Z","msg":"雖然俄佬都唔係好勁，但係支那換晒國產引擎先講啦<br />\n<br />\n部殲20仲要買緊人地上代引擎笑死人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aca33025845703f6bad721f2e18ab2ad0e2156e2","tid":925672,"uid":10890,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T02:59:43.000Z","msg":"F22/F35：我係話 在座各位"},{"pid":"4413f6d28ca429edda09c2e79d42c5e0f293da3a","tid":925672,"uid":10890,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T06:14:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HuVMxmc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHuVMxmc.png&h=25543555&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b62e899b380f0322b17960f2479841e4767f3821","tid":925672,"uid":39527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6904cf7ba116fb547c5010aa449e6f64be691c01","tid":925672,"uid":29080,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T02:30:33.000Z","msg":"打過，睇下邊個勁啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T06:20:57.000Z","msg":"岩呀 講咁多做乜鳩  覺得自己勁d咪出機去打過囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"189c07f4fbb8d6c980f22ad7901813de4d5f1168","tid":925672,"uid":83654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T06:22:20.000Z","msg":"核心引擘AL-31F 仲要進口...<br />\n繼續打飛機"},{"pid":"45d3eecaa9206f8c7e3124c7107360d08369a06f","tid":925672,"uid":36441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T06:24:25.000Z","msg":"人地都唔用鴨翼設計 但係丁20<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43c84b613f4f13afdce49361d536a43f05215d7b","tid":925672,"uid":15830,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T07:51:14.000Z","msg":"慘得過你連垃圾機都要山寨